{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":2000,"text":"Well, that's kind of an obvious statement up there."},{"time":4000,"text":"I started with that sentence about 12 years ago,"},{"time":7000,"text":"and I started in the context"},{"time":10000,"text":"of developing countries,"},{"time":12000,"text":"but you're sitting here from every corner of the world."},{"time":15000,"text":"So if you think of a map of your country,"},{"time":18000,"text":"I think you'll realize"},{"time":20000,"text":"that for every country on Earth,"},{"time":22000,"text":"you could draw little circles to say,"},{"time":24000,"text":"\"These are places where good teachers won't go.\""},{"time":28000,"text":"On top of that,"},{"time":30000,"text":"those are the places from where trouble comes."},{"time":33000,"text":"So we have an ironic problem --"},{"time":35000,"text":"good teachers don't want to go"},{"time":37000,"text":"to just those places where they're needed the most."}]},{"cues":[{"time":40000,"text":"I started in 1999"},{"time":43000,"text":"to try and address this problem with an experiment,"},{"time":46000,"text":"which was a very simple experiment in New Delhi."},{"time":51000,"text":"I basically embedded a computer"},{"time":54000,"text":"into a wall of a slum in New Delhi."},{"time":58000,"text":"The children barely went to school, they didn't know any English --"},{"time":61000,"text":"they'd never seen a computer before,"},{"time":63000,"text":"and they didn't know what the internet was."},{"time":66000,"text":"I connected high speed internet to it -- it's about three feet off the ground --"},{"time":69000,"text":"turned it on and left it there."},{"time":71000,"text":"After this,"},{"time":73000,"text":"we noticed a couple of interesting things, which you'll see."},{"time":76000,"text":"But I repeated this all over India"},{"time":79000,"text":"and then through"},{"time":81000,"text":"a large part of the world"},{"time":83000,"text":"and noticed"},{"time":85000,"text":"that children will learn to do"},{"time":87000,"text":"what they want to learn to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":90000,"text":"This is the first experiment that we did --"},{"time":92000,"text":"eight year-old boy on your right"},{"time":94000,"text":"teaching his student, a six year-old girl,"},{"time":97000,"text":"and he was teaching her how to browse."},{"time":101000,"text":"This boy here in the middle of central India --"},{"time":105000,"text":"this is in a Rajasthan village,"},{"time":107000,"text":"where the children recorded their own music"},{"time":110000,"text":"and then played it back to each other"},{"time":113000,"text":"and in the process,"},{"time":115000,"text":"they've enjoyed themselves thoroughly."},{"time":117000,"text":"They did all of this in four hours"},{"time":119000,"text":"after seeing the computer for the first time."},{"time":122000,"text":"In another South Indian village,"},{"time":125000,"text":"these boys here"},{"time":127000,"text":"had assembled a video camera"},{"time":129000,"text":"and were trying to take the photograph of a bumble bee."},{"time":131000,"text":"They downloaded it from Disney.com,"},{"time":133000,"text":"or one of these websites,"},{"time":135000,"text":"14 days after putting the computer in their village."},{"time":141000,"text":"So at the end of it,"},{"time":143000,"text":"we concluded that groups of children"},{"time":145000,"text":"can learn to use computers and the internet on their own,"},{"time":148000,"text":"irrespective of who"},{"time":150000,"text":"or where they were."}]},{"cues":[{"time":153000,"text":"At that point, I became a little more ambitious"},{"time":156000,"text":"and decided to see"},{"time":159000,"text":"what else could children do with a computer."},{"time":162000,"text":"We started off with an experiment in Hyderabad, India,"},{"time":165000,"text":"where I gave a group of children --"},{"time":168000,"text":"they spoke English with a very strong Telugu accent."},{"time":171000,"text":"I gave them a computer"},{"time":173000,"text":"with a speech-to-text interface,"},{"time":175000,"text":"which you now get free with Windows,"},{"time":178000,"text":"and asked them to speak into it."},{"time":180000,"text":"So when they spoke into it,"},{"time":182000,"text":"the computer typed out gibberish,"},{"time":184000,"text":"so they said, \"Well, it doesn't understand anything of what we are saying.\""},{"time":186000,"text":"So I said, \"Yeah, I'll leave it here for two months."},{"time":188000,"text":"Make yourself understood"},{"time":190000,"text":"to the computer.\""},{"time":192000,"text":"So the children said, \"How do we do that.\""},{"time":194000,"text":"And I said,"},{"time":196000,"text":"\"I don't know, actually.\""},{"time":198000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":200000,"text":"And I left."},{"time":202000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":205000,"text":"Two months later --"},{"time":207000,"text":"and this is now documented"},{"time":209000,"text":"in the Information Technology"},{"time":211000,"text":"for International Development journal --"},{"time":213000,"text":"that accents had changed"},{"time":215000,"text":"and were remarkably close to the neutral British accent"},{"time":218000,"text":"in which I had trained the speech-to-text synthesizer."},{"time":221000,"text":"In other words, they were all speaking like James Tooley."},{"time":224000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":226000,"text":"So they could do that on their own."},{"time":228000,"text":"After that, I started to experiment"},{"time":230000,"text":"with various other things"},{"time":232000,"text":"that they might learn to do on their own."}]},{"cues":[{"time":234000,"text":"I got an interesting phone call once from Columbo,"},{"time":237000,"text":"from the late Arthur C. Clarke,"},{"time":239000,"text":"who said, \"I want to see what's going on.\""},{"time":241000,"text":"And he couldn't travel, so I went over there."},{"time":244000,"text":"He said two interesting things,"},{"time":246000,"text":"\"A teacher that can be replaced by a machine should be.\""},{"time":251000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":253000,"text":"The second thing he said was that,"},{"time":255000,"text":"\"If children have interest,"},{"time":257000,"text":"then education happens.\""},{"time":260000,"text":"And I was doing that in the field,"},{"time":262000,"text":"so every time I would watch it and think of him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":264000,"text":"(Video) Arthur C. Clarke: And they can definitely"},{"time":267000,"text":"help people,"},{"time":269000,"text":"because children quickly learn to navigate"},{"time":271000,"text":"the web and find things which interest them."},{"time":274000,"text":"And when you've got interest, then you have education."}]},{"cues":[{"time":277000,"text":"Sugata Mitra: I took the experiment to South Africa."},{"time":280000,"text":"This is a 15 year-old boy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":282000,"text":"(Video) Boy: ... just mention, I play games"},{"time":285000,"text":"like animals,"},{"time":288000,"text":"and I listen to music."}]},{"cues":[{"time":291000,"text":"SM: And I asked him, \"Do you send emails?\""},{"time":293000,"text":"And he said, \"Yes, and they hop across the ocean.\""},{"time":297000,"text":"This is in Cambodia,"},{"time":299000,"text":"rural Cambodia --"},{"time":302000,"text":"a fairly silly arithmetic game,"},{"time":305000,"text":"which no child would play inside the classroom or at home."},{"time":307000,"text":"They would, you know, throw it back at you."},{"time":309000,"text":"They'd say, \"This is very boring.\""},{"time":311000,"text":"If you leave it on the pavement"},{"time":313000,"text":"and if all the adults go away,"},{"time":315000,"text":"then they will show off with each other"},{"time":317000,"text":"about what they can do."},{"time":319000,"text":"This is what these children are doing."},{"time":321000,"text":"They are trying to multiply, I think."},{"time":324000,"text":"And all over India,"},{"time":326000,"text":"at the end of about two years,"},{"time":328000,"text":"children were beginning to Google their homework."},{"time":331000,"text":"As a result, the teachers reported"},{"time":333000,"text":"tremendous improvements in their English --"},{"time":335000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":339000,"text":"rapid improvement and all sorts of things."},{"time":341000,"text":"They said, \"They have become really deep thinkers and so on and so forth."},{"time":344000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":347000,"text":"And indeed they had."},{"time":349000,"text":"I mean, if there's stuff on Google,"},{"time":351000,"text":"why would you need to stuff it into your head?"},{"time":355000,"text":"So at the end of the next four years,"},{"time":357000,"text":"I decided that groups of children can navigate the internet"},{"time":360000,"text":"to achieve educational objectives on their own."}]},{"cues":[{"time":363000,"text":"At that time, a large amount of money"},{"time":365000,"text":"had come into Newcastle University"},{"time":367000,"text":"to improve schooling in India."},{"time":370000,"text":"So Newcastle gave me a call. I said, \"I'll do it from Delhi.\""},{"time":373000,"text":"They said, \"There's no way you're going to handle"},{"time":375000,"text":"a million pounds-worth of University money"},{"time":378000,"text":"sitting in Delhi.\""},{"time":380000,"text":"So in 2006,"},{"time":382000,"text":"I bought myself a heavy overcoat"},{"time":384000,"text":"and moved to Newcastle."},{"time":387000,"text":"I wanted to test the limits"},{"time":389000,"text":"of the system."},{"time":391000,"text":"The first experiment I did out of Newcastle"},{"time":393000,"text":"was actually done in India."},{"time":395000,"text":"And I set myself and impossible target:"},{"time":398000,"text":"can Tamil speaking"},{"time":401000,"text":"12-year-old children"},{"time":403000,"text":"in a South Indian village"},{"time":406000,"text":"teach themselves biotechnology"},{"time":408000,"text":"in English on their own?"},{"time":410000,"text":"And I thought, I'll test them, they'll get a zero --"},{"time":413000,"text":"I'll give the materials, I'll come back and test them --"},{"time":415000,"text":"they get another zero,"},{"time":417000,"text":"I'll go back and say, \"Yes, we need teachers for certain things.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":421000,"text":"I called in 26 children."},{"time":423000,"text":"They all came in there, and I told them"},{"time":425000,"text":"that there's some really difficult stuff on this computer."},{"time":427000,"text":"I wouldn't be surprised if you didn't understand anything."},{"time":430000,"text":"It's all in English, and I'm going."},{"time":433000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":435000,"text":"So I left them with it."},{"time":437000,"text":"I came back after two months,"},{"time":439000,"text":"and the 26 children marched in looking very, very quiet."},{"time":441000,"text":"I said, \"Well, did you look at any of the stuff?\""},{"time":444000,"text":"They said, \"Yes, we did.\""},{"time":446000,"text":"\"Did you understand anything?\" \"No, nothing.\""},{"time":449000,"text":"So I said,"},{"time":451000,"text":"\"Well, how long did you practice on it"},{"time":453000,"text":"before you decided you understood nothing?\""},{"time":455000,"text":"They said, \"We look at it every day.\""},{"time":458000,"text":"So I said, \"For two months, you were looking at stuff you didn't understand?\""},{"time":460000,"text":"So a 12 year-old girl raises her hand and says,"},{"time":462000,"text":"literally,"},{"time":465000,"text":"\"Apart from the fact that improper replication of the DNA molecule"},{"time":468000,"text":"causes genetic disease,"},{"time":470000,"text":"we've understood nothing else.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":472000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":474000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":481000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":484000,"text":"It took me three years to publish that."},{"time":486000,"text":"It's just been published in the British Journal of Educational Technology."},{"time":489000,"text":"One of the referees who refereed the paper said,"},{"time":492000,"text":"\"It's too good to be true,\""},{"time":495000,"text":"which was not very nice."},{"time":497000,"text":"Well, one of the girls had taught herself"},{"time":499000,"text":"to become the teacher."},{"time":501000,"text":"And then that's her over there."},{"time":511000,"text":"Remember, they don't study English."},{"time":526000,"text":"I edited out the last bit when I asked, \"Where is the neuron?\""},{"time":529000,"text":"and she says, \"The neuron? The neuron,\""},{"time":531000,"text":"and then she looked and did this."},{"time":534000,"text":"Whatever the expression, it was not very nice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":537000,"text":"So their scores had gone up from zero to 30 percent,"},{"time":540000,"text":"which is an educational impossibility under the circumstances."},{"time":543000,"text":"But 30 percent is not a pass."},{"time":546000,"text":"So I found that they had a friend,"},{"time":548000,"text":"a local accountant, a young girl,"},{"time":550000,"text":"and they played football with her."},{"time":552000,"text":"I asked that girl, \"Would you teach them"},{"time":554000,"text":"enough biotechnology to pass?\""},{"time":556000,"text":"And she said, \"How would I do that? I don't know the subject.\""},{"time":558000,"text":"I said, \"No, use the method of the grandmother.\""},{"time":560000,"text":"She said, \"What's that?\""},{"time":562000,"text":"I said, \"Well, what you've got to do"},{"time":564000,"text":"is stand behind them"},{"time":566000,"text":"and admire them all the time."},{"time":569000,"text":"Just say to them, 'That's cool. That's fantastic."},{"time":571000,"text":"What is that? Can you do that again? Can you show me some more?'\""},{"time":574000,"text":"She did that for two months."},{"time":576000,"text":"The scores went up to 50,"},{"time":578000,"text":"which is what the posh schools of New Delhi,"},{"time":580000,"text":"with a trained biotechnology teacher were getting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":583000,"text":"So I came back to Newcastle"},{"time":585000,"text":"with these results"},{"time":587000,"text":"and decided"},{"time":589000,"text":"that there was something happening here"},{"time":591000,"text":"that definitely was getting very serious."},{"time":595000,"text":"So, having experimented in all sorts of remote places,"},{"time":598000,"text":"I came to the most remote place that I could think of."},{"time":601000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":604000,"text":"Approximately 5,000 miles from Delhi"},{"time":607000,"text":"is the little town of Gateshead."},{"time":609000,"text":"In Gateshead, I took 32 children"},{"time":612000,"text":"and I started to fine-tune the method."},{"time":615000,"text":"I made them into groups of four."},{"time":618000,"text":"I said, \"You make your own groups of four."},{"time":620000,"text":"Each group of four can use one computer and not four computers.\""},{"time":623000,"text":"Remember, from the Hole in the Wall."},{"time":626000,"text":"\"You can exchange groups."},{"time":628000,"text":"You can walk across to another group,"},{"time":630000,"text":"if you don't like your group, etc."},{"time":632000,"text":"You can go to another group, peer over their shoulders, see what they're doing,"},{"time":635000,"text":"come back to you own group and claim it as your own work.\""},{"time":638000,"text":"And I explained to them"},{"time":640000,"text":"that, you know, a lot of scientific research is done using that method."}]},{"cues":[{"time":643000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":645000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":652000,"text":"The children enthusiastically got after me and said,"},{"time":654000,"text":"\"Now, what do you want us to do?\""},{"time":656000,"text":"I gave them six GCSE questions."},{"time":659000,"text":"The first group -- the best one --"},{"time":661000,"text":"solved everything in 20 minutes."},{"time":663000,"text":"The worst, in 45."},{"time":666000,"text":"They used everything that they knew --"},{"time":668000,"text":"news groups, Google, Wikipedia,"},{"time":670000,"text":"Ask Jeeves, etc."},{"time":672000,"text":"The teachers said, \"Is this deep learning?\""},{"time":675000,"text":"I said, \"Well, let's try it."},{"time":677000,"text":"I'll come back after two months."},{"time":679000,"text":"We'll give them a paper test --"},{"time":681000,"text":"no computers, no talking to each other, etc.\""},{"time":683000,"text":"The average score when I'd done it with the computers and the groups"},{"time":685000,"text":"was 76 percent."},{"time":687000,"text":"When I did the experiment, when I did the test,"},{"time":689000,"text":"after two months, the score"},{"time":692000,"text":"was 76 percent."},{"time":695000,"text":"There was photographic recall"},{"time":697000,"text":"inside the children,"},{"time":699000,"text":"I suspect because they're discussing with each other."},{"time":702000,"text":"A single child in front of a single computer"},{"time":704000,"text":"will not do that."},{"time":706000,"text":"I have further results,"},{"time":708000,"text":"which are almost unbelievable,"},{"time":710000,"text":"of scores which go up with time."},{"time":712000,"text":"Because their teachers say"},{"time":714000,"text":"that after the session is over,"},{"time":716000,"text":"the children continue to Google further."}]},{"cues":[{"time":719000,"text":"Here in Britain, I put out a call"},{"time":721000,"text":"for British grandmothers,"},{"time":723000,"text":"after my Kuppam experiment."},{"time":725000,"text":"Well, you know,"},{"time":727000,"text":"they're very vigorous people, British grandmothers."},{"time":729000,"text":"200 of them volunteered immediately."},{"time":731000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":733000,"text":"The deal was that they would give me"},{"time":736000,"text":"one hour of broadband time,"},{"time":738000,"text":"sitting in their homes,"},{"time":740000,"text":"one day in a week."},{"time":742000,"text":"So they did that,"},{"time":744000,"text":"and over the last two years,"},{"time":746000,"text":"over 600 hours of instruction"},{"time":748000,"text":"has happened over Skype,"},{"time":750000,"text":"using what my students call the granny cloud."},{"time":753000,"text":"The granny cloud sits over there."},{"time":756000,"text":"I can beam them to whichever school I want to."}]},{"cues":[{"time":765000,"text":"(Video) Teacher: You can't catch me."},{"time":767000,"text":"You say it."},{"time":770000,"text":"You can't catch me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":773000,"text":"Children: You can't catch me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":776000,"text":"Teacher: I'm the gingerbread man."}]},{"cues":[{"time":779000,"text":"Children: I'm the gingerbread man."}]},{"cues":[{"time":781000,"text":"Teacher: Well done. Very good ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":789000,"text":"SM: Back at Gateshead,"},{"time":791000,"text":"a 10-year-old girl gets into the heart of Hinduism"},{"time":793000,"text":"in 15 minutes."},{"time":795000,"text":"You know, stuff which I don't know anything about."},{"time":801000,"text":"Two children watch a TEDTalk."},{"time":803000,"text":"They wanted to be footballers before."},{"time":805000,"text":"After watching eight TEDTalks,"},{"time":807000,"text":"he wants to become Leonardo da Vinci."}]},{"cues":[{"time":810000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":813000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":816000,"text":"It's pretty simple stuff."}]},{"cues":[{"time":818000,"text":"This is what I'm building now --"},{"time":820000,"text":"they're called SOLEs: Self Organized Learning Environments."},{"time":823000,"text":"The furniture is designed"},{"time":825000,"text":"so that children can sit in front of big, powerful screens,"},{"time":828000,"text":"big broadband connections, but in groups."},{"time":831000,"text":"If they want, they can call the granny cloud."},{"time":834000,"text":"This is a SOLE in Newcastle."},{"time":836000,"text":"The mediator is from Pune, India."}]},{"cues":[{"time":838000,"text":"So how far can we go? One last little bit and I'll stop."},{"time":841000,"text":"I went to Turin in May."},{"time":845000,"text":"I sent all the teachers away from my group of 10 year-old students."},{"time":849000,"text":"I speak only English, they speak only Italian,"},{"time":852000,"text":"so we had no way to communicate."},{"time":854000,"text":"I started writing English questions on the blackboard."},{"time":858000,"text":"The children looked at it and said, \"What?\""},{"time":860000,"text":"I said, \"Well, do it.\""},{"time":862000,"text":"They typed it into Google, translated it into Italian,"},{"time":865000,"text":"went back into Italian Google."},{"time":867000,"text":"Fifteen minutes later --"},{"time":877000,"text":"next question: where is Calcutta?"},{"time":882000,"text":"This one, they took only 10 minutes."},{"time":889000,"text":"I tried a really hard one then."},{"time":892000,"text":"Who was Pythagoras, and what did he do?"},{"time":897000,"text":"There was silence for a while,"},{"time":899000,"text":"then they said, \"You've spelled it wrong."},{"time":901000,"text":"It's Pitagora.\""},{"time":908000,"text":"And then,"},{"time":910000,"text":"in 20 minutes,"},{"time":912000,"text":"the right-angled triangles began to appear on the screens."},{"time":914000,"text":"This sent shivers up my spine."},{"time":917000,"text":"These are 10 year-olds."},{"time":932000,"text":"Text: In another 30 minutes they would reach the Theory of Relativity. And then?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":935000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":937000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":946000,"text":"SM: So you know what's happened?"},{"time":948000,"text":"I think we've just stumbled across"},{"time":950000,"text":"a self-organizing system."},{"time":952000,"text":"A self-organizing system is one"},{"time":954000,"text":"where a structure appears"},{"time":956000,"text":"without explicit intervention from the outside."},{"time":959000,"text":"Self-organizing systems also always show emergence,"},{"time":962000,"text":"which is that the system starts to do things,"},{"time":964000,"text":"which it was never designed for."},{"time":966000,"text":"Which is why you react the way you do,"},{"time":968000,"text":"because it looks impossible."},{"time":971000,"text":"I think I can make a guess now --"},{"time":974000,"text":"education is self-organizing system,"},{"time":976000,"text":"where learning is an emergent phenomenon."},{"time":978000,"text":"It'll take a few years to prove it, experimentally,"},{"time":980000,"text":"but I'm going to try."},{"time":982000,"text":"But in the meanwhile, there is a method available."},{"time":985000,"text":"One billion children, we need 100 million mediators --"},{"time":988000,"text":"there are many more than that on the planet --"},{"time":990000,"text":"10 million SOLEs,"},{"time":992000,"text":"180 billion dollars and 10 years."},{"time":996000,"text":"We could change everything."}]},{"cues":[{"time":998000,"text":"Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1000000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}